# Brand Color Palette — Sage / Gold / Paper

> Source: CURSOR_HANDOFF.md — "Why sage primary: calm, sustainable care. Why gold: energy for milestones."

All UI must use these exact hex values. **Never** use Tailwind semantic color classes like `blue-500`, `gray-200`, `purple-*`, `red-*`, `green-*`, `yellow-*`, `indigo-*`, or `emerald-*`.

## Palette

| Role | Hex | Usage |
|------|-----|-------|
| Light sage | `#9DC1A5` | Tints, gradient starts, habit tile bg |
| Primary sage | `#79A98C` | CTAs, active states, links |
| Dark sage | `#5E8C6E` | Hover states, gradient ends |
| Deep sage | `#3E7E57` | Completion / done indicators |
| Sage ink | `#2E5641` | Text on sage backgrounds |
| **Gold** | `#E5B122` | XP bar, streak counter, milestones |
| Dark gold | `#C99A1A` | Gold hover / pressed |
| Peach | `#FAC7B3` | Break/rehab habit tile accent |
| Sky tile | `#AFD4DD` | Sleep/focus habit tile accent |
| Cream | `#F0E9CE` | Card borders, secondary backgrounds |
| Paper | `#F6F3E9` | Page backgrounds |
| Dark ink | `#1B1714` | Headings, body text |
| Warm gray | `#8A7F78` | Secondary text, labels |
| Muted | `#C5BDB6` | Placeholders, disabled |
| Dark card | `#2C2622` | Dark mode card surface |
| Dark border | `#3D3730` | Dark mode borders |
| Dark hover | `#4A433E` | Dark mode hover states |

## Rules

```tsx
// ❌ NEVER use Tailwind semantic colors
className="bg-blue-500 text-gray-700 border-green-200"
className="from-purple-50 to-indigo-100"

// ✅ ALWAYS use brand hex values
className="bg-[#79A98C] text-[#8A7F78] border-[#F0E9CE]"
className="from-[#9DC1A5] to-[#79A98C]"
```

## Common Patterns

```tsx
// CTA button
className="bg-[#79A98C] hover:bg-[#5E8C6E] text-white active:scale-[0.97]"

// Ghost/tint button
className="bg-[#79A98C]/10 text-[#79A98C] hover:bg-[#79A98C]/15"

// Card (light mode)
className="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[#F0E9CE]"

// Card (with dark mode)
className="bg-white dark:bg-[#2C2622] rounded-2xl border border-[#F0E9CE] dark:border-[#3D3730]"

// Page background
className="bg-[#F6F3E9] dark:bg-[#1B1714]"

// Progress bar track
className="bg-[#F0E9CE] dark:bg-[#3D3730]"

// XP / milestone progress fill
style={{ background: 'linear-gradient(90deg, #E5B122, #C99A1A)' }}

// Completion (done/checked)
className="bg-[#3E7E57] text-white"

// Streak counter
className="text-[#E5B122] font-semibold"

// Active bottom nav
className="text-[#79A98C]"

// Habit tile: break/rehab (peach)
style={{ borderLeftColor: '#FAC7B3', background: '#FAC7B315' }}

// Habit tile: sleep/focus (sky)
style={{ borderLeftColor: '#AFD4DD', background: '#AFD4DD15' }}

// Habit tile: build/movement (sage)
style={{ borderLeftColor: '#9DC1A5', background: '#9DC1A515' }}

// Input focus
className="focus:ring-[#79A98C] focus:border-[#79A98C]"
```

## Typography
- **Headlines / numbers**: `font-family: 'DM Sans'` (weight 700–800)
- **Body / labels**: Inter (default)
- Apply DM Sans inline: `style={{ fontFamily: "'DM Sans', sans-serif" }}`

## Never Use
- `shadow-xl`, `shadow-2xl`, `shadow-3xl` — use `shadow-sm` or none
- Any `bg-gray-*`, `text-gray-*`, `border-gray-*`
- Any `blue-*`, `purple-*`, `indigo-*`, `red-*`, `green-*`, `yellow-*`, `emerald-*`, `orange-*`, `pink-*`
- Hardcoded gradients unless using the palette hex values above
